Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:37.88,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Aku... Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.39,Utama,Atuk Haruto,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Terbuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:41.47,Utama,Atuk Haruto,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Lambat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:46.18,Utama,Atuk Haruto,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:48.83,Utama,Atuk Haruto,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Kenapa kamu teragak-agak di saat gentir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:52.96,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tak... Amakawa Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.70,Utama,Haruto,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Mii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:05.79,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Apa semua ingatan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:07.50,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Aku di dalam bas...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:10.22,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Bas? "Bas" tu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:13.50,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Adakah aku jadi gila sebab demam?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:14.67,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:19.69,Utama,Mamat A,0,0,0,,Eh, Rio? Kau dah bangun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:24.79,Utama,Mamat B,0,0,0,,Uish, hidup lagi eh kau?\NAku ingatkan kau dah mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:27.29,Utama,Kyokan,0,0,0,,Kau ni memang budak yang liat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:30.19,Utama,Kyokan,0,0,0,,Semalam kau terhuyung-hayang sebab demam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:34.53,Utama,Kyokan,0,0,0,,Hoi! Tinggalkan benda tu dekat bucu bilik.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:36.90,Utama,Kyokan,0,0,0,,Dan pastikan kau letak elok-elok.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:37.55,Utama,Mamat A,0,0,0,,Baik! {dahek still kasar ngok}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:43.37,Utama,Mamat B,0,0,0,,Apa pun, sepuluh keping emas memang berbaloi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:47.44,Utama,Kyokan,0,0,0,,Sepuluh keping emas untuk pengangkutan biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:49.57,Utama,Kyokan,0,0,0,,Walaupun kargo itu bukanlah bagus mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.86,Utama,Mamat B,0,0,0,,Betul juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:54.67,Utama,Mamat A,0,0,0,,Nampak sedap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:58.22,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Aku lapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.31,Utama,Mamat A,0,0,0,,Hei, Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:00.01,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:03.13,Utama,Mamat A,0,0,0,,Busuk tau. Pergi mandi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:05.01,Utama,Mamat A,0,0,0,,Kau buat makanan tak sedap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.85,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:25.97,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Amakawa Haruto tinggal\Ndi sebuah negara bernama "Jepun."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:28.24,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Berumur dua puluh tahun dan\Npelajar universiti.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:32.21,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Kemudian, nampaknya seperti ada\Nkemalangan jalan raya, dan... Dia mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:36.75,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kemalangan jalan raya?\NApa tu? Aku tak faham!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:38.67,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tak, aku faham, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:41.28,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Cukup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:42.27,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Akulah Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:47.05,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Demi membalas dendam akan Ibuku,\Naku tinggal di kawasan setinggan ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.38,Haruto,Rio ;5 tahun,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur4}Ibu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:52.14,Haruto,Rio ;5 tahun,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur4}Kenapa rambut saya dan ibu berwarna hitam?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:57.90,Haruto,Ibu Rio,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur4}Sebabnya, Rio, mungkin sebab\Nibu dan ayah datang dari tempat yang jauh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:01.97,Haruto,Rio ;5 tahun,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur4}Adakah mereka yang tinggal di tempat\Nyang jauh juga berambut hitam?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:07.63,Haruto,Ibu Rio,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur4}Ya. Ayah, atuk dan nenek kamu,\Nmereka semua berambut hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:12.72,Haruto,Rio ;5 tahun,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur4}Wah... Suatu hari nanti, saya teringin\Nberjumpa dengan atuk dan nenek!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:19.29,Haruto,Rio's mom,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur4}Haah kan, bila kamu dah besar nanti, ibu akan\Nbawa kamu ke sana. Tempat bernama Yagumo. {nanti dia dh power dia akan gi Yagumo}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.80,Haruto,Rio ;5 tahun,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur4}Betulkah? Ibu janji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:23.35,Haruto,Ibu Rio,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur4}Ya, ibu janji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.97,0:06:26.69,Haruto,Ibu Rio,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur4}R-Rio... {damn aq dh agak dh... gaya rambut kematian}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:28.79,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Ibu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:35.58,Utama,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Oi! Kamu di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:37.35,Utama,Kristina,0,0,0,,Busuknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:40.25,Utama,Roanna,0,0,0,,Kita tak patut menghampirinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:42.28,Utama,Roanna,0,0,0,,Tidak bagus untuk kesihatan kamu.{ermm, how?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:44.59,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Siapa mereka ni?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:47.36,Utama,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Hoi, kamu dengar tak?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:49.04,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Dengar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:52.93,Utama,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Kamu ada nampak seorang gadis berambut ungu muda?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:55.40,Utama,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Lebih kurang sebaya dengan kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:06:57.12,Utama,Kristina,0,0,0,,Tolong jujur dengan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:58.41,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Entah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:07:02.59,Utama,Celia,0,0,0,,Semua, saya tak rasa dia akan\Njawab kalau kamu tanya sebegitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:04.33,Utama,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Celia-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:08.00,Utama,Celia,0,0,0,,Serahkan kepada saya ya? Vanessa-sama. {ni baru la beradab, aq dgr pun cair hahaha}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:10.36,Utama,Celia,0,0,0,,Maaf kerana kami memeranjatkan kamu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.60,Utama,Celia,0,0,0,,Apa nama kamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:15.23,Utama,Celia,0,0,0,,Nama saya Celia. {Cellia yo? Cellia ya!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:17.23,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Rio...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:20.19,Utama,Celia,0,0,0,,{\t(800,0,0.4,\3c&H937041&)}Rio? Nama yang aneh sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:22.14,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ibu bapa aku pendatang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:25.84,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Oo... Sebab itu rambut kamu berwarna hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:29.32,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Apa pun, Rio, saya mahu tanya beberapa soalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:32.95,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Fasal gadis berambut ungu muda?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.39,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tak pernah nampak.
Dialogue: -1,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.78,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Yakah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:38.57,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Mula dari sini kawasan setinggan, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:39.81,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ya, betul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:40.94,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Besar tak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:43.42,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Apa maksud kamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:46.42,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kami mesti mencari dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.63,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Lebih baik kamu jangan pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:53.60,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Sini bukanlah tempat yang sesuai untuk gadis\Nberbaju indah seperti kamu patut pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.35,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Berbaju indah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:08:01.31,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Apa jenis pakaian yang biasa\Ndipakai oleh gadis di kawasan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:03.33,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Jenis apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:07.07,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Sama seperti orang biasa,\Ncuma compang-camping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:09.03,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:10.03,Utama,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Celia-kun...{dia panggil Celia kun?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:13.47,Utama,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, kita patut kembali\Nmenukar pakaian dan datang semula.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:16.55,Utama,Kristina,0,0,0,,Apa yang maksud kamu?\NKalau kita tak cepat, dia akan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:17.89,Utama,Roanna,0,0,0,,Betul tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:21.36,Utama,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Tapi, kita bukan bergerak atas gerakan rasmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:24.28,Utama,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Kalau kita silap langkah dan membuat kekacauan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:27.21,Utama,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Pasti Kristina-sama tak mahu ia berlaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.93,Utama,Kristina,0,0,0,,J-Jadi marilah kita segera tukar baju dan kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:33.81,Utama,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Celia-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:37.39,Utama,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Untuk kepastian, boleh kamu\Ncari tindak balas sihir di sekitar sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:39.31,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:41.80,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur4}Area...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:41.80,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(960,940)\fscy62\fscx66\blur4}Kawasan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:47.66,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur4}Search!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:47.66,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(960,940)\fscy66\fscx66\blur4}Gelintar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.35,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.91,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Eh, kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:03.42,Utama,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Ada apa-apa dengan budak itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:07.52,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Nampaknya dia mempunyai\Njumlah kuantiti sihir yang banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:10.17,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Dia mempunyai potensi untuk menggunakan sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:13.84,Utama,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Ooo. Pernah juga berlaku pada beberapa anak yatim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:16.10,Utama,Kristina,0,0,0,,Dia ada kuasa sihir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:20.23,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Sihir? Cahaya yang aneh ini adalah sihir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:22.28,Utama,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Dan tindak balas yang lain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:23.60,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Malangnya tiada.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:28.52,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Tindak balas sihir yang dapat ditangkap\Ndengan carian hanyalah kita dan dia sahaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:29.39,Utama,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Begitukah. {hmm jap, aq rasa dlm novel dia x de jumpa Celia dulu, waktu dh angkat }
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:32.36,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Nampaknya, dia pasti ada di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:34.63,Atas,Vanessa; latar blkg,0,0,0,,Kita masih lagi tiada bukti yang kukuh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:34.63,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:38.21,Atas,Vanessa; latar blkg,0,0,0,,buat masa sekarang ini, kita perlu\Nbersiap tukar pakaian dan pergi sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:38.21,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,mereka tak boleh nampak cahaya ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.47,Utama,Celia,0,0,0,,Nampaknya begitulah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.37,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Oh! Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:45.50,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Bayaran untuk maklumat. Terimalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:48.91,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Selamat tinggal, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:50.55,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:57.46,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Duit perak besar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:58.44,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Sebanyak ini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:23.21,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Aku dah balik—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:55.11,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Si-siapa dia ni?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:56.36,Aishia,Aishia,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.78,Aishia,Aishia,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Masa sudah suntuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:03.34,Aishia,Aishia,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Od, dan cara menggunakan sihir,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.08,Aishia,Aishia,0,0,0,,{\blur4}saya akan ajarkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:07.40,Aishia,Aishia,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Ingatlah perasaan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:10.59,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,C-Cara menggunakan sihir?
